def max_occurred_integer(L, R, N, maxx):
    maxx = maxx - 10
    result = [0] * maxx
    for i in range(N):
        l = L[i]
        u = R[i] + 1
        result[u] += -1
        result[l] += 1
    for i in range(1, maxx):
        result[i] = result[i] + result[i - 1]
    high = max(result)
    val = result.index(high)
    return val
